3T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2062905/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2062905/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最初，以為講我，嚇了一跳～自我意識太強了，俗稱自大！哈<br />\n但我筆名確是香港小說／香港小說人。<br />\n<br />\n不過，也不怕醜，進來打個招呼。<br />\n連登的連載，是家中一名學生幫ＰＯ。<br />\n她沒留神，在小說第一帖便ＰＯ了另一個討論網的出處，不夠一分鐘，便得了一個負評，她怕我生氣。<br />\n我說：沒關係！其實，哪個討論網都不會客觀，好像水火不融一樣。<br />\n比喻：連登定位：黃營、曱甴、廢柴公屋仔。<br />\n香討則是：藍營、五毛軍營、黑警、自私精。<br />\n<br />\n但我仍然是香港人，只盡量在最後的光輝歲月，享受創作自由。<br />\n肉麻講句：我愛香港。這些藍黃對壘，我都是抽離看。<br />\n<br />\n請各位仁兄仁姐，幫忙看一下，小女文筆如何，謝謝。<br />\n曾經，另一個討論網有讀者說我文筆不錯，怎不ＰＯ內地小說網，市場大，讀者群多。<br />\n當時，我只笑說：你想我被槍斃咩！哈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"老實講，冇睇內容，但啲文筆真係睇唔落去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0ef6547ac40b0a76cfd17541f206b94c64009b","tid":2073388,"uid":58375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2473e3b2393ac9896a82334e4dc95723fb761718","tid":2073388,"uid":352753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"入咗谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新手自薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《相愛十年》post1:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1974011/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1974011/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"0179fa759678b0c5177f0ed20e43c0d5f925e340","tid":2073388,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2473e3b2393ac9896a82334e4dc95723fb761718","tid":2073388,"uid":352753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"入咗谷<img src=\"/assets/face